---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy – Card Games by Vanikar"
  description="Privacy Policy for Card Games by Vanikar LLC. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal-date">Effective Date: January 1, 2026 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Last Updated: January 1, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <p>
          Vanikar LLC (&ldquo;Vanikar,&rdquo; &ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;) operates the <strong>Card Games</strong> mobile application
          (the &ldquo;App&rdquo;) and the website at <a href="https://vanikar.games">vanikar.games</a> (the &ldquo;Site&rdquo;).
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect information about you when you use our
          App and Site (collectively, the &ldquo;Services&rdquo;). By using our Services you agree to this Privacy Policy.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Account data:</strong> display name, email address, and password when you create an account.</li>
          <li><strong>Profile data:</strong> avatar, club membership, and in-game preferences you set voluntarily.</li>
          <li><strong>Communications:</strong> messages you send to our support team.</li>
          <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> if you purchase virtual currency or premium features, payment is processed by Apple App Store or Google Play; we do not store full card numbers.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Device identifiers:</strong> device type, operating system version, and a randomly generated device ID.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> game sessions, features accessed, match results, and session duration.</li>
          <li><strong>Log data:</strong> IP address, crash reports, and diagnostic information.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> aggregated, de-identified statistics about how players use the App, collected via first-party tooling.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Information from Third Parties</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>If you sign in with Apple or Google, we receive your name and email address from that provider.</li>
          <li>Club or tournament organisers may share limited data to administer competitions.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Create and manage your account and provide the Services.</li>
          <li>Match you with online opponents and power real-time multiplayer features.</li>
          <li>Operate clubs, leaderboards, and tournaments.</li>
          <li>Process in-app purchases and fulfil virtual-currency transactions.</li>
          <li>Send transactional emails (account confirmation, password reset, match invitations).</li>
          <li>Detect cheating, fraud, and Terms of Service violations.</li>
          <li>Improve the App through aggregated analytics and crash reporting.</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations and enforce our Terms of Service.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

        <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>With other players:</strong> your display name, avatar, and game statistics are visible to players you play with or compete against.</li>
          <li><strong>Club members:</strong> if you join a club, members can see your username and club-related stats.</li>
          <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> trusted vendors who help us operate the Services under confidentiality obligations.</li>
          <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> when required by law, court order, or to protect the safety of any person.</li>
          <li><strong>Business transfers:</strong> in connection with a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, subject to standard confidentiality protections.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain account data for as long as your account is active plus up to 90 days after deletion for dispute resolution. Anonymised analytical data may be retained indefinitely.</p>

        <h2>5. Security</h2>
        <p>We use industry-standard safeguards including TLS 1.2+ encryption in transit and access controls limiting employee access to personal data. No method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.</p>

        <h2>6. Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our Services are not directed to children under 13 (or under 16 in the EEA). If you believe a child has provided us personal information, please contact us and we will promptly delete it.</p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        <p>Depending on where you live, you may have the right to access, correct, delete, or port your data, or to restrict or object to certain processing. Email <a href="mailto:privacy@vanikar.games">privacy@vanikar.games</a> to exercise these rights. You may also delete your account in the App via <em>Settings &rarr; Account &rarr; Delete Account</em>.</p>

        <h2>8. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>The App may link to third-party services with their own privacy policies. We are not responsible for their practices.</p>

        <h2>9. International Transfers</h2>
        <p>Our servers are located in the United States and the European Union. We implement appropriate safeguards (e.g., Standard Contractual Clauses) where required.</p>

        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>Material changes will be announced in the App or by email at least 14 days before they take effect. Continued use after the effective date constitutes acceptance.</p>

        <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Vanikar LLC</strong><br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@vanikar.games">privacy@vanikar.games</a><br />
          Web: <a href="https://vanikar.games">vanikar.games</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
